    "en": {
      "title": "Arjuna summons Aloysius",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "W. M. Colombo Additional Magistrate T. ordered Mendis and the company to appear in court today (02) regarding non-payment of tax amount of 167 crore rupees owed to the Inland Revenue Department. N. L. Mr. Ilangasinghe has issued summons to Mr. Arjuna Aloysius.",
        "Accordingly, summonses have been issued to A. Prince Tower, Alfred House, Colombo 03. J. To Mr. Aloysius.",
        "No. 309/5, Negombo Road, Welisara Address W. M. The Inland Revenue Department had filed this case last year 2021 that Mendis and the company had failed to pay an amount of Rs. 1,678,795,049/= as income tax due to the Inland Revenue Department."
      ],
